&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in hunting and closing net new logos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to strategically map out and break into large scale organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious, motivated, and driven as a sales person&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bold on the phones and creative in your emails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to sit up to 6 hours, traveling to and from client sites via auto, train, or air, up to 30% of the time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
